{"tid":2136071,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇gaming laptop 推介？","createTime":"2020-08-01T23:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T23:09:25.000Z","uid":49201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ed519b447dd27af3b3546dec05495eb9563eee5","tid":2136071,"uid":49201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T23:06:21.000Z","msg":"筆直20K左右<br />\n因工作關係年中成日都要出差幾個月，自己又鍾意打機，想買部portable既。<br />\n但平時係香港個陣就會外接mon, keyboard, sound card咁，所以呢幾part完全唔在意。<br />\n主要希望散熱好，性能勁，重量都冇咩所謂<br />\n<br />\n暫時睇啱部MSI GE75(i9-10980HK/RTX2080S-8G)<br />\n但太耐冇追新機，唔知而家有咩牌子咩型號抵玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以開po問下巴打們有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a677dd8544575f583be9967f48ffdd39c0d2252","tid":2136071,"uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T23:08:09.000Z","msg":"去Notebook討論區TOPIC問<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2129231/page\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2129231/page</a>"},{"pid":"a480b7ae9cf916bf2b131cd3afcbb8c458c1e416","tid":2136071,"uid":49201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a677dd8544575f583be9967f48ffdd39c0d2252","tid":2136071,"uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T23:08:09.000Z","msg":"去Notebook討論區TOPIC問<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2129231/page\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2129231/page</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T23:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}